:: CombatLosePirate [no-teleport no-saving]
<<combatResults>>

You wake up on your back, covered in bruises and staring at the stars. You're not quite sure how you managed to \
survive, be it luck, or fate, but you count your blessings. Perhaps next time you won't risk your neck for \
the crew of this blasted ship... or at least, you'll come better prepared.

Still, despite the pain, it appears that the crew did appreciate your efforts. 

