:: CombatFleePirate [no-teleport no-saving]
You quickly run back into your cabin and slam the door shut behind you. With frentic energy \
you start shoving your meagre furnishings against the door trying to blockade it and then \
finally add your own bodyweight to the mess.

The sounds of fighting outside intensifies and the cannon blasts continue for a good quarter of an hour. \
You're certain that the @@color:cyan;Salty Mermaid@@ is starting to list to the port, but before you \
can ponder how far it is to swim to shore, a shout goes up outside! It appears that the crew was \
victorious after all.

Hopefully no one noticed your cowardice...

